================================================================================
EXP 2 — Two-stage: LightGBM + per-StoreDept Ridge residual correction
================================================================================
Hypothesis: A per-SD linear model on LightGBM residuals captures systematic
            bias for each store-department combination.

---
r2:      0.999673
wmae:    424.82
seconds: ~200
---
Status: DISCARD  (Ridge overfit on training residuals; generalised poorly)

================================================================================
EXP 3 — LightGBM + XGBoost blend + EWM(alpha=0.3) feature
================================================================================
Change  : Added exponential weighted moving average of sales (alpha=0.3) as
          a new feature. Blended LightGBM and XGBoost predictions; optimised
          blend weight on validation set.
Insight : Different error geometries (MAE vs RMSE objectives) produce
          complementary predictions — blending reduces variance.

---
r2:      0.999811   (+0.000037 vs baseline)
mae:     175.21
rmse:    415.83
wmae:    314.72      (-41.25 vs baseline)
mape:    0.4901
seconds: 247.4
---
Status: KEEP ✓

================================================================================
EXP 4 — 3-model blend + multi-alpha EWM + holiday interaction features
================================================================================
Change  : Added EWM with 3 alphas (0.1, 0.3, 0.6). Added holiday×lag
          interaction features: hol_x_lag1, xmas_x_lag52. Added Sales_accel
          (lag1 − roll4_mean) and log-ratio feature. Added LGB2 (seed=123,
          lr=0.02). Used scipy Nelder-Mead to optimise 3-way blend weights.
Insight : Multi-alpha EWM gives the model smoothed sales signals at different
          time scales. Holiday×lag interactions explicitly encode the uplift
          pattern for each holiday type.

---
r2:      0.999853   (+0.000079 vs baseline)
mae:     163.08
rmse:    388.71
wmae:    248.01      (-107.96 vs baseline)
mape:    0.4611
seconds: 421.4
---
Status: KEEP ✓

================================================================================
